data.description: NO HOA! Enjoy your new beautiful home with great square footage and a finished basement. Make yourself at home in the comfortable living room with fireplace or entertain guests in the dining room with a view to the living room from the kitchen. Enjoy the huge back deck and covered front porch oversized--perfect for family and friends to hang out. Spacious master bedroom and en suite and large walk-in closets.  Four bedrooms. This beauty sits in a Cul-De-Sac with plenty of privacy. Real hardwood floors in the living room and kitchen. New roof 4 or 5 years old, HVAC NEW, Water heater NEW, tile in hallway bathroom, new toilets, fenced in back yard with a beautiful burn pit. The master is on the main level. Separate shower and tub in master bath. Great schools close, Paulding school districts. shopping and dining. You better act quickly, this one will be gone fast! Call today to schedule an appointment.
